Sri Lanka’s Central Bank Maintains 8.5% GDP Growth For 2011

-- B y   A n u s h a   O n d a a t j i e   a n d   A s a n t h a   S i r i m a n n e
-- 
2011-04-11T07:25:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-11/sri-lanka-s-central-bank-maintains-8-5-gdp-growth-for-2011.html
Sri Lanka ’s central bank will
maintain its 2011 growth forecast of 8.5 percent even as the
South Asian island nation is likely to face a “challenging
year,” central bank Governor Nivard Cabraal told reporters in
 Colombo  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
